JWT token authentication 

run node middleware/token.js to generate the authentication token copy the token , Use Postman ,hit endpt with
- {
  "Authorization": "Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN"
}


The following routes are protected and require a valid JWT token in the Authorization header:

GET /api/gadgets
POST /api/gadgets
PATCH /api/gadgets/:id
DELETE /api/gadgets/:id
POST /api/gadgets/:id/self-destruct
GET /gadgets?status={status}